	<h2 class="title"><a href="http://wearechange.org/gun-control-activist-swears-forgot-carrying-gun-visiting-school/" title="Permanent Link to Gun control activist swears he forgot he was carrying gun while visiting school">Gun control activist swears he forgot he was carrying gun while visiting school</a></h2>



	
		
	<p class="post-meta"><img src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/b4302c4784acbfbfa10ba2a02da1d155?s=50&amp;d=&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-50 avatar-default' height='50' width='50' style='width: 50px; height: 50px;' alt='avatar' />Posted  by <a href="http://wearechange.org/author/ebarlow/" title="Posts by Eric Barlow" rel="author">Eric Barlow</a> on February 10, 2014</p>


	


	


	<p><a href="http://dailycaller.com/2014/02/10/gun-stun-gun-control-activist-swears-he-forgot-he-was-carrying-gun-while-visiting-school/">www.dailycaller.com</a></p>
<p><a href="http://wearechange.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/guncontrolactivistarrested.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-21868" alt="guncontrolactivistarrested" src="http://wearechange.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/guncontrolactivistarrested-600x257.jpg" width="600" height="257" /></a></p>
<p>A Buffalo, N.Y. community activist who is well known locally for pushing for a highly restrictive 2013 gun control law has been arrested for — wait for it — carrying a gun illegally at a public elementary school.</p>
<p>The arrested gun-control advocate, Dwayne Ferguson, caused quite a scene at Harvey Austin Elementary School, <a href="http://wivb.com/2014/02/07/reports-of-man-with-gun-near-elementary-school/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">reports local CBS affiliate WIVB.</a></p>


