	<h2 class="title"><a href="http://wearechange.org/ralph-nader-on-the-two-party-dictatorship-awlaki-occupy-wall-st/" title="Permanent Link to Ralph Nader on the Two Party Dictatorship, Awlaki, Occupy Wall St">Ralph Nader on the Two Party Dictatorship, Awlaki, Occupy Wall St</a></h2>



	
		
	<p class="post-meta"><img src='http://wearechange.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/abby.jpg' class='avatar avatar-50 avatar-default' height='50' width='50' style='width: 50px; height: 50px;' alt='avatar' />Posted  by <a href="http://wearechange.org/author/abby/" title="Posts by abby" rel="author">abby</a> on October 11, 2011</p>


	


	


	<span class="vvqbox vvqyoutube" style="width:600px;height:344px;"><span id="vvq-10043-youtube-1"><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vMobQqiYKI4"><img src="http://img.youtube.com/vi/vMobQqiYKI4/0.jpg" alt="YouTube Preview Image" /></a></span></span>
<p>Abby Martin of Media Roots talks to political activist and former  presidential candidate Ralph Nader about Project Censored, the landscape  of media censorship, the establishment co-opting of the tea party, the  two party dictatorship in the US, Obama&#8217;s exacerbation of Bush era  policies and the recent assassination of Anwar al-Awlaki.</p>
<span class="vvqbox vvqyoutube" style="width:600px;height:344px;"><span id="vvq-10043-youtube-2"><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L_43dqkKqjk"><img src="http://img.youtube.com/vi/L_43dqkKqjk/0.jpg" alt="YouTube Preview Image" /></a></span></span>
<p>Q and A with Ralph Nader after his talk at the Hillside Club in Berkeley, CA on October 1, 2011. Nader talks about the Occupy Wall Street protests, Gandhi&#8217;s &#8216;Seven Deadly Sins&#8217;, media reform, his presidential candidacy and how we need to continue fighting for change.</p>
<p><a title="http://www.mediaroots.org" href="http://www.mediaroots.org/">http://www.mediaroots.org</a></p>


